Sentencas: We reported nano-structured Ag modified Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.6Fe0.4O3-delta (Ag@BSCF) cathode for solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) that is prepared by vacuum assisted electroless deposition technique.
Titulo: Ag decorated (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells prepared by electroless silver deposition

Sentencas: We show that the concentration of Ag can be easily adjusted by tuning the deposition time without altering the perovskite structure of the pristine BSCF.
Titulo: Ag decorated (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells prepared by electroless silver deposition

Sentencas: The effect of Ag loading on the electrochemical performance of the material has been systematically studied by varying the Ag loading and the working condition (oxygen partial pressure).
Titulo: Ag decorated (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells prepared by electroless silver deposition

Sentencas: An optimized electrode performance is observed with an Ag loading of similar to 2 wt%.
Titulo: Ag decorated (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells prepared by electroless silver deposition

Sentencas: We demonstrate that the presence of Ag significantly reduces the electrode ohmic resistance and enhances the catalytic O-2 reduction performance of the BSCF cathode.
Titulo: Ag decorated (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells prepared by electroless silver deposition
